imgs.alt: Art of Loki from Persona 5 from the waist up and his arms spread wide. Loki is a human and geometric shaped being with a chaotic black and white stripe pattern over his body, two horns coming out of his eyes, and many braided black and red strands.

Art of Loki from Persona 5 from the ankles up and his arms spread wide. Loki is a human and geometric shaped being with a chaotic black and white stripe pattern over his body, two horns coming out of his eyes, and many braided black and red strands.
